creator: ToTee Global
descriptionHtml:
🌸 Are you a big fan of Japanese manga? 🌸
💁 Would you like to create your own sweet anime doll avatar? 💁

✨ Now you can make your own anime characters and become a cool doll avatar designer with our game: Anime Avatar Maker: Sweet Doll. Bring your talent for making hundred of anime doll avatars, become a cool doll designer and write your own story today! ✨

💌 WHAT IS UNIQUE IS THIS DRESS-UP GAME 💌

👘 MANGA CHARACTER DESIGN 👘
Countless unique outfits, hair, accessories and items designed exclusively for anime fans. Impossible to find them in other fashion games.

️🏆 BATTLE AND WORLDWIDE RANKING ️🏆
Random battle with thousands of anime doll avatar designers around the world in this game. Do you consider yourself a person with good taste? Join the battle and find out your rank in the manga world ranking today!

🌺 VIVID GRAPHICS DESIGN 🌺
Bringing players super imaginative and creative avatar games, anime style, exquisite screen design, unique anime characters, a large number of customization options to write your own dream story!

👗👘 WORLD OF SWEET FASHION ITEM 👠💄
In this game, we constantly update fashion items with the most special and trendy designs. Which fashion style do you like? Sweet, feminine or trendy? Here we have all the options for you to feel free to create your own personality

😍 Do not hesitate to join one of the most exciting fashion experience with Anime Avatar Maker: Sweet Doll. Join our sweet anime world become character creator, avatar maker and make your own character rightnow!
descriptionShort: Explore the dream fashion world and design your own sweet anime doll avatars
